### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### List all students
GET http://localhost:3000/api/students

### Create a student
POST http://localhost:3000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Eve",
  "last_name": "Ho",
  "email": "eve.ho@example.edu",
  "department_id": 1,
  "enrollment_year": 2025
}

### Enroll student 1 in course 2
POST http://localhost:3000/api/enrollments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": 1,
  "course_id": 2,
  "semester": "2025-Fall"
}

### List enrollments for student 1
GET http://localhost:3000/api/enrollments?student_id=1

